Ilaitasheikinok le sirit


1  Enkiroroto nasipa ena inchere, te neyieu oltung'ani neaku olaitasheikinoni le sirit, naa eyieunoto sidai. 
2   Eishiaakino olaitasheikinoni le sirit, nemeeta eleyiata olee le nkitok nabo loo nkiririkinot, naa ng'en, pirisut, naa aminin, neyiolo aiteng'enisho, 
3  nememera, nemearisho, kake oltung'ani supat, neme olaishankarrani, nemenyor impesai. 
4  Neitasheiki olmarei lenye aitobiraki, neitoning'isho inkera enyena, pee eyanyitisho too nkoitoi pooki. 
5  Amaa te nemeyiolo oltung'ani aitasheiki enkaji enye, kaji eiko te neing'or esirit e Enkai?


6  Enyor neme ilo oibelekenye det pee merup kewan to Iwuasa nebatatakino enkiguana e shetani. 
7  Neme ina ake eishiaakino neeta errepet te lelo ootii boo pee medoiki ake atua esulare o rreshet le shetani.

Ilaretok tiatua esirit


8  Neijia ake sii etiu ilaisiaayiak, inchoo emut nabo nemeitoki aaing'ashing'ash too nkirorot, neme ilooitabaitie enaisho, nemeeta olorok le dupoto, 
9  inchoo eibung enkirukoto to ltau owang. 
10  Nchoo sii eng'asi aatem ninche, ore ake peyie eitisipi nchere meeta ileyiat, nchoo easisho anaa ilaisiaayiak. 
11  Neijia ake sii eikununo inkituaak, nchoo emut nabo, neme inaakurrisho kake inoo nkiririkinot, naaisiligayu too mbaa pooki. 
12  Nchoo laisiaayiak eaku olmoruo le nkitok nabo, neitasheiki sii ninche inkera enye o nkajijik enye aaitobiraki. 
13  Amu ore lelo ooasisho aaitobiraki anaa ilaisiaayiak naa ketum errepet sidai maate, netum enkitieunoto kitok ti atua enkirukoto natii atua Kristo Yesu.

Enkisudoroto kitok


14  Aisilig ajo kalotu enitii asieku, kake aasiraki kuna kiteng'enat peyie, 
15  te naimutie niyiolou enaishiaakino neas oltung'ani ti atua enkaji e Enkai. Naa ninye esirit e Enkai naishu, ninye eng'ape, o lkitamanyunoto loo sipat. 
16  Kitejo iyiook tukul inchere, kitok oleng enkisudoroto e nkirukoto ang:

Eibalunyeki ninye to sesen,

neitadedeyieki ninye te Nkiyang'et

nedol ilmalaika,

nelikiori too loreren,

neiruk enkop,

neyae ninye shumata te nkitoo.

